│ true successor should not be the current block (PrevBB). Both successors      │
│ should be placeholders to be filled later.\n- Manually setting successor(0)   │
│ to nullptr after passing a non-null block leads to a partially constructed    │
│ branch with inconsistent state.\n\nAs a result, the successor edges are not   │
│ properly established when successors are created, leaving pred.sdiv.if        │
